{
  "stem": "19921.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 158.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So she almost fainted when she saw me, seriously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Of course, my house was demolished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I did not have a house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When I came in, there was no home there anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a businessman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what he had, he had two trucks-- two trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was a moving truck, you know, for people to move from one city or from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like a moving truck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other one was a general transportation truck to move goods from the railroad station to the businesspeople.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had that in 1932.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In 1932, and 1933, '34.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later, the business, for some reason, got bad, and he had to get rid of the trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he went to a horse transportation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he had four, four pairs of horses, and the people which [INAUDIBLE] those horses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the same thing-- is strictly for transportation, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because there was a railroad station, and there were a lot of businesses which needed the goods transported from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's what he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he did this thing here till he passed away in 1937.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as far as I remember, things were doing pretty good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, basic things were doing pretty good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He lost a lot of money when he-- and during the 1932 depression, between '32 and '34.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He lost a lot of money there, and that's the reason he has to get rid of the trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But otherwise than that, it was basic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know if they had any savings or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But nobody was starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Everybody was dressed nicely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And everybody was, thank God, was healthy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's far-- far as I know--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--up to that point.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
